            <listitem>
                <para>The new <parameter>monitoring()</parameter> and <parameter>monitoring-welf()</parameter> sources have been added to <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="monitor-syslog-ng-statistics-metrics"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <command>syslog-ng-query</command> application is available in &abbrev; 7.0.2, as part of the <command>syslog-ng-ctl</command> utility. For details, see <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-admin" targetptr="syslog-ng-ctl-query"/>.</para>
